* MOSFET CS amplifier
VDD vdd 0 DC 11.93
Vin in 0 AC 1
Cin in gate 3.3u
RG1 vdd gate 1Meg
RG2 gate 0 560k
RD vdd drain 15k
M1 drain gate source 0 NMOS1
RS source 0 6.8k
Cout drain out 47u
